; font-size: 18px; line-height: 18px; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 18px; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;四大省电模块&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sub_title&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: left; display: block; font-size: 21px; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: left; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;空调设计省电模块、运行控制省电模块、元件与技术省电模块、空调待机省电模块，从头到脚打造绿色风。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://image.haier.com/cn/consumer/air_conditioners/W020140513389207906107.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;327&quot; width=&quot;490&quot; oldsrc=&quot;W020140513389207906107.jpg&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px none; outline: none; float: right; height: 327px; width: 490px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 18px; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;强力模式&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sub_title&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: left; display: block; font-size: 21px; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: left; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;总觉得舒适温度来得不够快？升温或降温的时间可不可以再短一点？ ＊启动强力模式，热交换速度更快，居室内可以迅速升降温。 ＊启动安静模式，风速更柔和，运转声音更低，静享舒适空间。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://image.haier.com/cn/consumer/air_conditioners/W020140513418752390068.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;327&quot; width=&quot;490&quot; oldsrc=&quot;W020140513418752390068.jpg&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px none; outline: none; float: left; height: 327px; width: 490px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 18px; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;智能一键通&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sub_title&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: left; display: block; font-size: 21px; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: left; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;＊智能调温 智能将室温调至24℃，也可自由调节 ＊智能模式 根据室温自动切换运行模式 ＊智能调速 根据室温与设定温度的温差自动调整 ＊智能除湿 根据室内湿度情况，自动切换除湿模式 ＊智能除霜 根据室外机实际结霜情况，智能作出除霜判断&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://image.haier.com/cn/consumer/air_conditioners/W020140512417600135203.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;327&quot; width=&quot;490&quot; oldsrc=&quot;W020140512417600135203.jpg&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px none; outline: none; float: right; height: 327px; width: 490px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 18px; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;人性化睡眠&lt;